summary: A Trident staff with a projectile ice and absorb health enchantment
descriptionHtml:
This simple little mod adds a Trident staff with a projectile ice and absorb health enchantment. Due to popular request a melee version has been added. They both share the custom model and texture. They can be found on a dead body just North of Solitude on a small island near the Light House. Special thanks to Gray-Wolf Jack for showing me how to set up the thrusting melee animation. Please do not redistribute.

The textures on the trident were made using source material from CGTextures.com. These images may not be redistributed by default, please visit www.cgtextures.com for more information.
author: Matthew_Lane1992
